					<h2 class="esri-text__title">Use the story conversion helper</h2>
				
				
				<div class="esri-text__description richtext-container trailer-0">
					<p>Instead of rebuilding existing Esri Story Maps stories, try the classic story conversion helper—a tool that helps copy text and media to ArcGIS StoryMaps.</p>

				</div>
